snippet.textDisplay:
Hence proved no one can beat Coke Studio Pakistan.
Coke Studio Pakistan nay fresh singers (jin ka naam tak kisi nay nahi suna tha) ko lay kar bhi kamal kia.
.
No disrespect laiken agar India start say apnay folk songs, cultural and classical music ko agay lay kar chalta to itni disappointment na hoti, Indian music industry k pas itna paisa, market and resources honay k bad bhi un ko Coke Studio mein wo success nahi mil pa rahi jo milni chahiye, first it was because of the mindset k agar super hit singers ko lain gay to success milay gi, in other words Bollywood taste, but nakam huway, 
.
Coke Studio Pakistan ki beauty hi ye hai k wo apnay culture, folk music, classical music ko own kartay hein and proudly represent kartay hein, apni roots say juray hein, so called modernism k chakar mein wo nasha kar k nahi bethay bal k acha music produce kar rahay hein
